{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"c82a45ea03c9396b83d2e6","title":"LVGL 主桌面六模式与语音卡片 UI 移植总结","desc":"","updated":1780371367055,"created":1780371330023,"custom":{},"fname":"开发记录.2026-05-06_LVGL主桌面六模式与语音卡片UI移植总结","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"256d065ef0cb0e7caa6189df03193d3a","links":[{"from":{"fname":"开发记录.项目交接资料","id":"6d428def14b8ffdc828f43","vaultName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":88,"column":12,"offset":3024},"end":{"line":88,"column":53,"offset":3065},"indent":[]},"value":"开发记录.2026-05-06_LVGL主桌面六模式与语音卡片UI移植总结"},{"from":{"fname":"开发记录.项目开发记录总纲","id":"62ff4545e5f1373c5cfe01","vaultName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":34,"offset":1640},"end":{"line":22,"column":75,"offset":1681},"indent":[]},"value":"开发记录.2026-05-06_LVGL主桌面六模式与语音卡片UI移植总结"}],"anchors":{"lvgl-主桌面六模式与语音卡片-ui-移植总结":{"type":"header","text":"LVGL 主桌面六模式与语音卡片 UI 移植总结","value":"lvgl-主桌面六模式与语音卡片-ui-移植总结","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"1-背景":{"type":"header","text":"1. 背景","value":"1-背景","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2},"2-主桌面六模式图标--多语言标题":{"type":"header","text":"2. 主桌面：六模式图标 + 多语言标题","value":"2-主桌面六模式图标--多语言标题","line":23,"column":0,"depth":2},"21-行为说明":{"type":"header","text":"2.1 行为说明","value":"21-行为说明","line":25,"column":0,"depth":3},"22-新增--调整文件":{"type":"header","text":"2.2 新增 / 调整文件","value":"22-新增--调整文件","line":30,"column":0,"depth":3},"23-语言刷新":{"type":"header","text":"2.3 语言刷新","value":"23-语言刷新","line":41,"column":0,"depth":3},"24-可选模式图标微动效":{"type":"header","text":"2.4 可选：模式图标微动效","value":"24-可选模式图标微动效","line":46,"column":0,"depth":3},"3-二级桌面语音卡片-ui录音--生成--错误":{"type":"header","text":"3. 二级桌面：语音卡片 UI（录音 / 生成 / 错误）","value":"3-二级桌面语音卡片-ui录音--生成--错误","line":52,"column":0,"depth":2},"31-布局对象":{"type":"header","text":"3.1 布局对象","value":"31-布局对象","line":54,"column":0,"depth":3},"32-状态与-api":{"type":"header","text":"3.2 状态与 API","value":"32-状态与-api","line":60,"column":0,"depth":3},"33-动效录音验证":{"type":"header","text":"3.3 动效（录音验证）","value":"33-动效录音验证","line":68,"column":0,"depth":3},"34-进入二级桌面逻辑节选":{"type":"header","text":"3.4 进入二级桌面逻辑（节选）","value":"34-进入二级桌面逻辑节选","line":73,"column":0,"depth":3},"4-按键与业务联动":{"type":"header","text":"4. 按键与业务联动","value":"4-按键与业务联动","line":80,"column":0,"depth":2},"41-button_controlc":{"type":"header","text":"4.1 button_control.c","value":"41-button_controlc","line":82,"column":0,"depth":3},"42-audio_uploadc":{"type":"header","text":"4.2 audio_upload.c","value":"42-audio_uploadc","line":87,"column":0,"depth":3},"43-audio_result_waitc--h":{"type":"header","text":"4.3 audio_result_wait.c / .h","value":"43-audio_result_waitc--h","line":96,"column":0,"depth":3},"44-mqtt_backend_binary_rxc":{"type":"header","text":"4.4 mqtt_backend_binary_rx.c","value":"44-mqtt_backend_binary_rxc","line":102,"column":0,"depth":3},"5-语音识别跑偏代码对比结论备忘":{"type":"header","text":"5. 语音识别「跑偏」：代码对比结论（备忘）","value":"5-语音识别跑偏代码对比结论备忘","line":109,"column":0,"depth":2},"6-编译与产物":{"type":"header","text":"6. 编译与产物","value":"6-编译与产物","line":117,"column":0,"depth":2},"7-涉及文件清单汇总":{"type":"header","text":"7. 涉及文件清单（汇总）","value":"7-涉及文件清单汇总","line":125,"column":0,"depth":2},"8-后续可做事项可选":{"type":"header","text":"8. 后续可做事项（可选）","value":"8-后续可做事项可选","line":152,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"x43b2g7jzkj4yilx9xlswpb","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"lvgl-主桌面六模式与语音卡片-ui-移植总结\">LVGL 主桌面六模式与语音卡片 UI 移植总结<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lvgl-主桌面六模式与语音卡片-ui-移植总结\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"lvgl-主桌面六模式与语音卡片-ui-移植总结-1\">LVGL 主桌面六模式与语音卡片 UI 移植总结<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lvgl-主桌面六模式与语音卡片-ui-移植总结-1\"></a></h1>\n<p><strong>日期</strong>：2026-05-06<br>\n<strong>参考快照</strong>：<code>applications.-wjz 参数已经写好了-0506/</code><br>\n<strong>目标工程</strong>：<code>applications/</code>（BK7252n + RT-Thread + LVGL）<br>\n<strong>编译命令</strong>：<code>scons --beken=bk7252n</code></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-背景\">1. 背景<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1-背景\"></a></h2>\n<p>将快照目录中与 <strong>主桌面六种业务模式展示</strong>、<strong>多语言文案</strong>、<strong>长按语音键后的录音 / 生成等待 / 错误反馈界面</strong> 相关的实现，合并进当前仓库的 <code>applications</code>，并保持与 <code>device_config</code> 语言 ID（0～20）一致。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-主桌面六模式图标--多语言标题\">2. 主桌面：六模式图标 + 多语言标题<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2-主桌面六模式图标--多语言标题\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"21-行为说明\">2.1 行为说明<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#21-行为说明\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>主桌面中间区域由原先「整屏 <code>desktop_modes</code> 大图」改为 <strong>135×135 卡片</strong>：当前模式展示 <strong>100×100 <code>mode_icon_*</code> BMP</strong> + <strong><code>ui_strings</code> 模式标题</strong>（随语言切换）。</li>\n<li>六种模式的英文 key（供 MQTT / <code>audio_upload_set_mode</code>）不变：<code>anime</code>、<code>cartoon</code>、<code>ink_wash</code>、<code>line_art</code>、<code>simple_drawing</code>、<code>sketch</code>。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"22-新增--调整文件\">2.2 新增 / 调整文件<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#22-新增--调整文件\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>路径</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>applications/images/mode_icons_bmp.c</code> / <code>.h</code></td><td>六模式小图标资源（可由 <code>tools/scripts/gen_mode_icons_bmp.py</code> 再生成）</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/images/SConscript</code></td><td><code>SrcRemove(src, 'desktop_modes_bmp.c')</code>，避免与大图重复占 Flash</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/pages/ui_strings.c</code> / <code>.h</code></td><td>21 语言 × 全文案表（含 <code>UI_STR_MODE_*</code>、语音/错误/页脚等）</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/pages/lv_example_meter.c</code></td><td>模式槽位、<code>main_mode_panel_apply</code>、<code>desktop_refresh_center</code> 等</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/device_config.c</code> / <code>.h</code></td><td><code>device_config_get_language_id()</code>；保存语言后调用 <code>lv_desktop_refresh_language()</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/pages/lv_example_meter.h</code></td><td><code>lv_desktop_refresh_language()</code> 声明</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h3 id=\"23-语言刷新\">2.3 语言刷新<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#23-语言刷新\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>lv_desktop_refresh_language()</code>：异步到 LVGL 线程，<code>ui_strings_sync_from_device_config()</code> 后重建模式槽位文案并刷新当前屏。</li>\n<li><code>device_config.c</code> 内提供 <strong><code>__attribute__((weak)) void lv_desktop_refresh_language(void)</code></strong> 空实现；<code>lv_example_meter.c</code> 提供强符号覆盖，避免无 UI 时链接失败。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"24-可选模式图标微动效\">2.4 可选：模式图标微动效<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#24-可选模式图标微动效\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>宏 <strong><code>LV_MODE_PANEL_ICON_ANIM</code></strong>（默认 <code>0</code>）：为 <code>1</code> 时六模式图标可有 bounce/sway/透明度动画（与 0506 一致，默认关闭省 RAM）。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-二级桌面语音卡片-ui录音--生成--错误\">3. 二级桌面：语音卡片 UI（录音 / 生成 / 错误）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#3-二级桌面语音卡片-ui录音--生成--错误\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"31-布局对象\">3.1 布局对象<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#31-布局对象\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code>s_sec_voice</code></strong>：全屏透明容器，内嵌与主桌面同风格的语音卡片（135×135）。</li>\n<li><strong><code>s_sec_img</code></strong>：仅用于 <strong>WS 热敏预览图</strong>（二进制结果下发后）。</li>\n<li>去掉二级桌面上 <strong>录音 / 生成中 / 失败</strong> 的 BMP chroma 大图路径，改为纯 LVGL 绘制 + <code>ui_strings</code>。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"32-状态与-api\">3.2 状态与 API<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#32-状态与-api\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>枚举 <strong><code>voice_ui_state_t</code></strong>（定义于 <code>lv_example_meter.h</code>）：<code>RECORDING</code>、<code>GENERATING</code>、<code>ERR_OFFLINE</code>、<code>ERR_BUSY</code>、<code>ERR_MIC</code>、<code>ERR_UPLOAD</code>、<code>ERR_TOO_SHORT</code>、<code>ERR_TIMEOUT</code>、<code>ERR_CLOUD</code>、<code>ERR_PRINT</code>、<code>ERR_CRC</code>、<code>ERR_PREVIEW</code>、<code>ERR_QR_PREVIEW</code> 等。</li>\n<li><strong><code>lv_desktop_voice_set_state(voice_ui_state_t)</code></strong>：任意线程可调用，内部 <code>lv_async_call</code> 派发到 LVGL，映射 <code>s_result_view</code> 并 <code>second_desktop_refresh_center()</code>。</li>\n<li><strong><code>lv_desktop_request_secondary_with_voice_state(voice_ui_state_t)</code></strong>：设置 pending 后请求进入二级桌面，用于 MQTT 离线等「先进页面再刷错误卡」的场景。</li>\n<li><strong><code>lv_desktop_request_show_generating_image()</code></strong> → <code>VOICE_UI_GENERATING</code>（旋转 Arc + 文案）。</li>\n<li><strong><code>lv_desktop_request_show_failure_image()</code></strong> → <code>VOICE_UI_ERR_CLOUD</code>（通用云端失败文案）。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"33-动效录音验证\">3.3 动效（录音验证）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#33-动效录音验证\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>录音态</strong>：红点卡片；宏 <strong><code>LV_VOICE_RECORDING_USE_PULSE</code></strong>（默认 <strong><code>0</code></strong>）控制是否启用透明度脉冲。默认关闭以降低录音阶段 LVGL 负载，便于验证 ASR 是否受 UI 动画影响。</li>\n<li><strong>生成等待</strong>：Arc 旋转动画（未在本次默认关闭）。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"34-进入二级桌面逻辑节选\">3.4 进入二级桌面逻辑（节选）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#34-进入二级桌面逻辑节选\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>首次进入：若无 pending 语音状态，默认 <strong><code>VOICE_UI_RECORDING</code> + <code>UI_RESULT_BG</code></strong>，刷新语音卡片。</li>\n<li>已在二级桌面时再次触发进入：重置为录音卡片（与长按清 WS 预览等行为对齐）。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"4-按键与业务联动\">4. 按键与业务联动<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#4-按键与业务联动\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"41-button_controlc\">4.1 <code>button_control.c</code><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#41-button_controlc\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>P37 长按</strong>：若 MQTT 未连接 → <code>lv_desktop_request_secondary_with_voice_state(VOICE_UI_ERR_OFFLINE)</code>；若 <code>audio_upload_start()</code> 失败 → <code>VOICE_UI_ERR_BUSY</code>；否则 <strong><code>audio_upload_start()</code> → <code>lv_desktop_request_enter_secondary_page()</code></strong>（顺序与改 UI 前成功路径一致）。</li>\n<li><strong>P36 长按</strong>：仍为 <strong>SN 二维码热敏打印</strong>；在 <code>audio_result_wait</code> 锁定或打印中时不响应（与 0506 分支一致）。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"42-audio_uploadc\">4.2 <code>audio_upload.c</code><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#42-audio_uploadc\"></a></h3>\n<p>在 worker 中增加 UI 反馈（不改变 Opus / 分包格式）：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Opus 未就绪或 reset 失败 → <code>VOICE_UI_ERR_MIC</code></li>\n<li>分包发送失败 → <code>VOICE_UI_ERR_UPLOAD</code></li>\n<li>尾包发送失败 → <code>VOICE_UI_ERR_UPLOAD</code></li>\n<li>从未发出任何分包（录音过短）→ <code>VOICE_UI_ERR_TOO_SHORT</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"43-audio_result_waitc--h\">4.3 <code>audio_result_wait.c</code> / <code>.h</code><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#43-audio_result_waitc--h\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>超时 → <code>VOICE_UI_ERR_TIMEOUT</code></li>\n<li><code>on_result_error</code> → <code>VOICE_UI_ERR_CLOUD</code></li>\n<li>新增 <strong><code>audio_result_wait_on_result_abort(task_id, voice_ui_state_t reason)</code></strong>，用于打印线程创建失败等需带具体原因的场景。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"44-mqtt_backend_binary_rxc\">4.4 <code>mqtt_backend_binary_rx.c</code><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#44-mqtt_backend_binary_rxc\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>整包 CRC 校验失败：<code>audio_result_wait_clear()</code> + <code>lv_desktop_voice_set_state(VOICE_UI_ERR_CRC)</code></li>\n<li>打印线程创建失败：<code>audio_result_wait_on_result_abort(..., VOICE_UI_ERR_PRINT)</code></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"5-语音识别跑偏代码对比结论备忘\">5. 语音识别「跑偏」：代码对比结论（备忘）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#5-语音识别跑偏代码对比结论备忘\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code>applications/audio/audio_upload.c</code></strong> 与快照 <strong><code>applications.-wjz …/audio_upload.c</code></strong> 在录音循环、<code>opus_encode</code>、包头、<code>publish_chunk</code>、<code>audio_upload_start</code> 等层面 <strong>一致</strong>；本次主要为 <strong>错误分支增加 <code>lv_desktop_voice_set_state</code></strong>。</li>\n<li>若识别变差与本次改动相关，更可疑的是 <strong>录音期间 LVGL 负载</strong>（二级桌面重建 + 动画），而非上传字节流被改坏。</li>\n<li>验证手段之一：<strong>默认关闭录音红点脉冲</strong>（<code>LV_VOICE_RECORDING_USE_PULSE=0</code>），对比识别效果后再决定是否恢复或继续关闭生成阶段 Arc。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"6-编译与产物\">6. 编译与产物<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#6-编译与产物\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>成功执行：<code>scons --beken=bk7252n</code></li>\n<li>生成文件迁至 <strong><code>out/</code></strong>（如 <code>rtthread.bin</code>、<code>all_4M.*.bin</code> 等，以当前 <code>config.json</code> 为准）。</li>\n<li>移除主桌面 <code>desktop_modes_bmp</code> 编译、移除二级 BMP chroma 解码路径后，text 段相对「大图 + chroma」版本有所变化；<code>failure_bmp</code> / <code>record_generating_bmp</code> 若仍参与链接但未再被 UI 引用，可考虑在 <code>applications/images/SConscript</code> 中 <code>SrcRemove</code> 以进一步瘦身（可选）。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"7-涉及文件清单汇总\">7. 涉及文件清单（汇总）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#7-涉及文件清单汇总\"></a></h2>\n<pre><code>applications/images/mode_icons_bmp.c\napplications/images/mode_icons_bmp.h\napplications/images/SConscript\napplications/pages/ui_strings.c\napplications/pages/ui_strings.h\napplications/pages/lv_example_meter.c\napplications/pages/lv_example_meter.h\napplications/mqtt_backend/device_config.c\napplications/mqtt_backend/device_config.h\napplications/button_control/button_control.c\napplications/audio/audio_upload.c\napplications/audio/audio_result_wait.c\napplications/audio/audio_result_wait.h\napplications/mqtt_backend/mqtt_backend_binary_rx.c\n</code></pre>\n<p>参考对照目录：</p>\n<pre><code>applications.-wjz 参数已经写好了-0506/applications/...\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"8-后续可做事项可选\">8. 后续可做事项（可选）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#8-后续可做事项可选\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>若确认 ASR 与动画无关：将 <strong><code>LV_VOICE_RECORDING_USE_PULSE</code></strong> 改回 <code>1</code> 恢复脉冲动效。</li>\n<li>如需进一步减负：录音阶段也可关闭 <strong>生成界面 Arc</strong>，或单独增加宏控制。</li>\n<li>清理未使用的 <code>failure_bmp.c</code> / <code>record_generating_bmp.c</code> 编译项以节省 Flash。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>本文档随仓库迭代更新；若目录策略变更，可将本文迁移至统一「开发记录」目录并保持单一来源。</p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlink